        "content": "<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><i>First sticheron at \"Lord, I have cried\" of Vespers of Sts Cosmas and Damian (November 1), </i><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:15.3333px;\"><i><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;font-family:&quot;Valkyrie A&quot;, &quot;Source Serif&quot;;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:center;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:break-spaces;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Plagal of Second Mode</span></i></span></p>",
